Field.Name: TaxKeyword
Field.Description: Enterprise Keywords are shared with other users and applications to allow for ease of search and filtering, as well as metadata consistency and reuse

Field.Name: CompatibleManagedProperties
Field.Description: Enter the names of the managed properties that you would like to use this Filter Display Template with. The managed properties with names that start with the values you enter will be able to use this Display Template.

Field.Name: ManagedPropertyMapping
Field.Description: Enter the slots and the managed properties that map to the slots. This field will be used to determine which managed properties are retrieved from SharePoint Search when you are using this Display Template. Use the format "slot name":"property name", separated by commas.

Field.Name: CrawlerXSLFile
Field.Description: Add an XSL file to be used to generate HTML when crawlers are viewing the page.

Field.Name: DisplayTemplateLevel
Field.Description: Select the level of data that this display template expects and is designed to display. This determines where this template will appear as a selectable option in configuration UIs.

Field.Name: CanvasContent1
Field.Description: This column stores the content of the authoring canvas in a site page.

Field.Name: TargetControlType
Field.Description: Select the search controls that will use this Display Template.

Field.Name: CompatibleSearchDataTypes
Field.Description: Select the Search managed property data types that this Filter Display Template will be used with. If you don't enter any values, the Display Template will be available for all data types.

Field.Name: LayoutWebpartsContent
Field.Description: This column stores the content of webparts in page layout in a site page.

Field.Name: TemplateHidden
Field.Description: Hide this Display Template where people select from an available list of search Display Templates.
